</table>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <strong>Stateless by design:</strong> The register deliberately has no database. All planning data lives in the council's BOPS system. The register is a read-only view that can be deployed, scaled, or replaced without affecting any data. This separation of concerns is a key architectural principle.
</div>
